{"tid":1429033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會 可唔可以每人講自己認為\"光復香港 時代革命\"既意思 延續上集","createTime":"2019-08-07T11:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:39:42.000Z","uid":170974,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2d882fa107fee45e51a42216c8bc873758530cda","tid":1429033,"uid":170974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"依家我地比人亂扣帽子 嘗試分化港獨同大中華人士 模糊我地既訴求<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n<br />\n呢八個字明明就係口號 用黎團結自己人<br />\n連口號都港獨緊？有口號就變質？<br />\n係咪示威連叫咩都要被管<br />\n我地有我地既解釋權 點解比人扣完帽子 我地就隻字不提呢<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n毛姨姨都幫手詮釋當中意思 你地斬腳指被沙蟲？"},{"pid":"11feeba1659f5951a363a65fe817dd5d48899da5","tid":1429033,"uid":170974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"72edbc474e0a2f5549050b8c60607348eb512a42","tid":1429033,"uid":281895,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"口號要解釋就唔係好口號"},{"pid":"3988d7803911ca2e5b74d1a0b10b0b9be814983d","tid":1429033,"uid":170974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"72edbc474e0a2f5549050b8c60607348eb512a42","tid":1429033,"uid":281895,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"口號要解釋就唔係好口號"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"口號係要凝聚 解釋係因為唔想比人廢言 誣衊 分化 港獨 大中華 破壞運動"},{"pid":"18aef881c22b036d4e24bdafc0cb7ce3f5ad5562","tid":1429033,"uid":170974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:02:45.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"2d6f7a9d4ec9e391b8c084d42474bc0135aaa6ed","tid":1429033,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"baa9808bc336c8d4954fced10d451cf582362df3","tid":1429033,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:03:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60c905143bf6cd76c5d401e92ece91a083ed3c1e","tid":1429033,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor